org.eclipse.persistence.json.bind.internal.unmarshaller

Class AdaptedObjectDeserializer<A,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.json.bind.internal.unmarshaller.AdaptedObjectDeserializer<A,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - adapted type, type to unmarshall JSOn into
    T - required type, typically type of the field, which is adapted to another type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.json.bind.serializer.JsonbDeserializer<T>, RuntimeTypeInfo, CurrentItem<T>

    public class AdaptedObjectDeserializer<A,T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements CurrentItem<T>, javax.json.bind.serializer.JsonbDeserializer<T>
    Decorator for an item which builds adapted type instance by a JsonbAdapter. After adapted item is finished building its instance is converted to field type object by calling adapter.
